{"tid":1486840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知我可唔可以幫和理非講幾句說話","createTime":"2019-08-19T04:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T10:59:48.000Z","uid":280474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07ed1170bd93c90ec2b2cebbcdec507eb75ff43c","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"無論係十八區遊行 以至係昨日818流水式集會<br />\n和理非都係出於擔心先係咁叫大家走啫<br />\n講真 大家昨晚11點幾仲留守喺夏愨道<br />\n學我老豆老母話齋 班狗要出嚟同你打過真係有曬理由<br />\n唔係幫警察 正正就係知道班黑社會已經泯滅人性<br />\n又headshot 又爆眼 又鳩射tg 都依然正義凜然<br />\n真係好好好擔心大家安全 語氣會先咁重先<br />\n大家點都唔想咁撚辛苦行咗5/6/7/8個鐘<br />\n然後聽日睇新聞又見到黑警暴力事件 真係會好痛心<br />\n仲要比班仆街藍絲打曬飛機話又有暴徒啊哈哈哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾撚唔抵啊大佬 <br />\n其實做和理非其實成日心掛掛都冇話唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在此 如果昨日有一時諗唔開語氣重咗嘅 我同各位手足講對唔住<br />\n希望大家明白勇武同和理非都有各自各嘅諗法<br />\n互相尊重 絕不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4924cf9957ba7c297a4de7a0136fc2591139329","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e2a15ac09d11dfa91d2a3f52ecec071175fb5b8b","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3226eb02c0488d6c3d2994d0630b3fe5dada433f","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed03970f859af31a3564cbdd5c425b38b736b3ab","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8377f9bf02b7b4dc8ac145c48497ddd945f3499e","tid":1486840,"uid":280474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"738a0a2f1b59b546733b208da1f8472a5b09